{"id":"p001","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p001-s0","tokens":[{"s":"全て","r":"すべて","v":"v0001"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"始まり","r":"はじまり","v":"v0002"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"忘れ","r":"わすれ","v":"v0003","lemma":"忘れる"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"し","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"ない"},{"s":"あの","v":"v0005"},{"s":"一言","r":"ひとこと","v":"v0006"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"It all began with one line I'll never forget."}}]}
{"id":"p002","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p002-s0","tokens":[{"s":"トレジャーハンター","v":"v0007"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"なろう","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"ぜ"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Let's become Treasure Hunters.","note":"なろう is the volitional of なる (\"to become\"); ぜ is a casual, assertive sentence-ending particle used mostly by men among friends. Together they form a confident, masculine \"let's…\" — closer to \"let's go become\" than a polite suggestion.","grammar":["g-volitional-ze"]}}]}
{"id":"p003","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p003-s0","tokens":[{"s":"昔","r":"むかし","v":"v0009"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"話","r":"はなし","v":"v0010"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"まだ","v":"v0011"},{"s":"僕達","r":"ぼくたち","v":"v0012"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"十","r":"じゅう","v":"v0013"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"満た","r":"みた","v":"v0014","lemma":"満ちる"},{"s":"ない"},{"s":"子供","r":"こども","v":"v0015"},{"s":"だった"},{"s":"頃","r":"ころ","v":"v0016"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"話","r":"はなし","v":"v0010"},{"s":"だ"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"It's a story from long ago — back when we hadn't even reached ten."}}]}
{"id":"p004","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p004-s0","tokens":[{"s":"いつも","v":"v0017"},{"s":"一緒","r":"いっしょ","v":"v0018"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"遊んでいた","r":"あそんでいた","v":"v0019","lemma":"遊ぶ"},{"s":"友人","r":"ゆうじん","v":"v0020"},{"s":"グループ","v":"v0021"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"一人","r":"ひとり","v":"v0022"},{"s":"──"},{"s":"幼馴染","r":"おさななじみ","v":"v0023"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"一人","r":"ひとり","v":"v0022"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"言った","r":"いった","v":"v0024","lemma":"言う"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"One of the friends I always played with — one of my childhood friends — said it."}}]}
{"id":"p005","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p005-s0","tokens":[{"s":"トレジャーハンター","v":"v0007"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"なろう","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Let's become Treasure Hunters."}},{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p005-s1","tokens":[{"s":"世界","r":"せかい","v":"v0025"},{"s":"各地","r":"かくち","v":"v0026"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"『"},{"s":"宝物殿","r":"ほうもつでん","v":"v0027"},{"s":"』"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"回り","r":"まわり","v":"v0028","lemma":"回る"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"富","r":"とみ","v":"v0029"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"栄光","r":"えいこう","v":"v0030"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"手","r":"て","v":"v0031"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"入れよう","r":"いれよう","v":"v0032","lemma":"入れる"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Let's tour the \"Treasuries\" scattered around the world and seize wealth and glory for ourselves."}}]}
{"id":"p006","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p006-s0","tokens":[{"s":"目指す","r":"めざす","v":"v0033"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"ただ","v":"v0034"},{"s":"一つ","r":"ひとつ","v":"v0035"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"世界","r":"せかい","v":"v0025"},{"s":"最強","r":"さいきょう","v":"v0036"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"英雄","r":"えいゆう","v":"v0037"},{"s":"だ"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"What we were aiming for was just one thing — to be the world's greatest heroes."}},{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p006-s1","tokens":[{"s":"俺達","r":"おれたち","v":"v0038"},{"s":"なら"},{"s":"……"},{"s":"この","v":"v0039"},{"s":"六人","r":"ろくにん","v":"v0040"},{"s":"なら"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"きっと","v":"v0041"},{"s":"なれる","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"If it's us — if it's the six of us — we can do it for sure."}}]}
{"id":"p007","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p007-s0","tokens":[{"s":"無鉄砲","r":"むてっぽう","v":"v0042"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"腕っ節","r":"うでっぷし","v":"v0043"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"強い","r":"つよい","v":"v0044"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"しかし","v":"v0045"},{"s":"勇敢","r":"ゆうかん","v":"v0046"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"男","r":"おとこ","v":"v0047"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"友達","r":"ともだち","v":"v0048"},{"s":"だった"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Reckless and scrappy, but brave — that's the kind of guy he was, our friend."}}]}
{"id":"p008","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p008-s0","tokens":[{"s":"何一つ","r":"なにひとつ","v":"v0049"},{"s":"根拠","r":"こんきょ","v":"v0050"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"ない"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"しかし","v":"v0045"},{"s":"キラキラ","v":"v0051"},{"s":"輝いていた","r":"かがやいていた","v":"v0052","lemma":"輝く"},{"s":"提案","r":"ていあん","v":"v0053"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"とても","v":"v0054"},{"s":"足","r":"あし","v":"v0055"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"速く","r":"はやく","v":"v0056","lemma":"速い"},{"s":"器用","r":"きよう","v":"v0057"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"友人","r":"ゆうじん","v":"v0020"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"賛同","r":"さんどう","v":"v0058"},{"s":"した","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"To this baseless but sparkling proposal, the swift, dexterous friend among us was the first to agree."}}]}
{"id":"p009","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p009-s0","tokens":[{"s":"本","r":"ほん","v":"v0059"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"読む","r":"よむ","v":"v0060"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"大好き","r":"だいすき","v":"v0061"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"友人","r":"ゆうじん","v":"v0020"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"おずおず","v":"v0062"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"それ","v":"v0063"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"追従","r":"ついじゅう","v":"v0064"},{"s":"し","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"少々","r":"しょうしょう","v":"v0065"},{"s":"口数","r":"くちかず","v":"v0066"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"少ない","r":"すくない","v":"v0067"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"頼り","r":"たより","v":"v0068"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"なる","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"友人","r":"ゆうじん","v":"v0020"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"大きく","r":"おおきく","v":"v0069","lemma":"大きい"},{"s":"頷いた","r":"うなずいた","v":"v0070","lemma":"頷く"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"The friend who loved reading went along with it sheepishly, and the quiet but reliable friend gave a firm nod."}}]}
{"id":"p010","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p010-s0","tokens":[{"s":"いつも","v":"v0017"},{"s":"後ろ","r":"うしろ","v":"v0071"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"ついてきていた","v":"v0072","lemma":"付いてくる"},{"s":"妹","r":"いもうと","v":"v0073"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"僕","r":"ぼく","v":"v0074"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"顔","r":"かお","v":"v0075"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"窺い","r":"うかがい","v":"v0076","lemma":"窺う"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"僕","r":"ぼく","v":"v0074"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"また","v":"v0077"},{"s":"それ","v":"v0063"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"賛成","r":"さんせい","v":"v0078"},{"s":"した","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"My little sister, who always tagged along behind us, glanced up at my face, and I, too, gave my approval."}}]}
{"id":"p011","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p011-s0","tokens":[{"s":"各地","r":"かくち","v":"v0026"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"遺跡","r":"いせき","v":"v0079"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"巡り","r":"めぐり","v":"v0080","lemma":"巡る"},{"s":"数々","r":"かずかず","v":"v0081"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"不思議","r":"ふしぎ","v":"v0082"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"宝具","r":"ほうぐ","v":"v0083"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"持ち帰る","r":"もちかえる","v":"v0084"},{"s":"トレジャーハンター","v":"v0007"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"今","r":"いま","v":"v0085"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"昔","r":"むかし","v":"v0009"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"花形","r":"はながた","v":"v0086"},{"s":"だ"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Treasure Hunters — the ones who tour ruins around the world and bring back all sorts of mysterious artifacts — have always been, and still are, the stars of the show."}}]}
{"id":"p012","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p012-s0","tokens":[{"s":"富","r":"とみ","v":"v0029"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"名誉","r":"めいよ","v":"v0087"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"力","r":"ちから","v":"v0088"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Wealth, renown, power."}}]}
{"id":"p013","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p013-s0","tokens":[{"s":"この","v":"v0039"},{"s":"世界","r":"せかい","v":"v0025"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"存在","r":"そんざい","v":"v0089"},{"s":"する","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"全て","r":"すべて","v":"v0001"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"手","r":"て","v":"v0031"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"入れ","r":"いれ","v":"v0032","lemma":"入れる"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"英雄","r":"えいゆう","v":"v0037"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"なる","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"のに"},{"s":"それほど","v":"v0090"},{"s":"手っ取り早い","r":"てっとりばやい","v":"v0091"},{"s":"方法","r":"ほうほう","v":"v0092"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"ない"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"There's no shortcut faster than that to grasping everything this world has to offer and becoming a hero."}}]}
{"id":"p014","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p014-s0","tokens":[{"s":"もちろん","v":"v0093"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"リスク","v":"v0094"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"ある","v":"v0095"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Of course, there are risks."}}]}
{"id":"p015","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p015-s0","tokens":[{"s":"凶悪","r":"きょうあく","v":"v0096"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"トラップ","v":"v0097"},{"s":"や"},{"s":"恐ろしい","r":"おそろしい","v":"v0098"},{"s":"魔物","r":"まもの","v":"v0099"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"幻影","r":"げんえい","v":"v0100"},{"s":"により"},{"s":"倒れた","r":"たおれた","v":"v0101","lemma":"倒れる"},{"s":"ハンター","v":"v0102"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"話","r":"はなし","v":"v0010"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"いくらでも","v":"v0103"},{"s":"あった","v":"v0095","lemma":"ある"},{"s":"し"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"友達","r":"ともだち","v":"v0048"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"そんな","v":"v0104"},{"s":"提案","r":"ていあん","v":"v0053"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"する","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"きっかけ","v":"v0105"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"なった","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"ある","v":"v0106"},{"s":"ハンター","v":"v0102"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"語る","r":"かたる","v":"v0107"},{"s":"冒険譚","r":"ぼうけんたん","v":"v0108"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"中","r":"なか","v":"v0109"},{"s":"でも"},{"s":"残酷","r":"ざんこく","v":"v0110"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"シーン","v":"v0111"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"いくつも","v":"v0112"},{"s":"あった","v":"v0095","lemma":"ある"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Stories of Hunters cut down by vicious traps, terrible monsters, or illusions were a dime a dozen, and the very adventurer's tale that had set off our friend's proposal had no shortage of brutal scenes either."}}]}
{"id":"p016","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p016-s0","tokens":[{"s":"だが","v":"v0113"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"その","v":"v0114"},{"s":"程度","r":"ていど","v":"v0115"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"リスク","v":"v0094"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"僕達","r":"ぼくたち","v":"v0012"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"冒険心","r":"ぼうけんしん","v":"v0116"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"ついた","v":"v0117","lemma":"付く"},{"s":"火","r":"ひ","v":"v0118"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"消し止める","r":"けしとめる","v":"v0119"},{"s":"事","r":"こと","v":"v0120"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"できなかった","v":"v0121","lemma":"できる"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"But risk on that scale wasn't enough to put out the fire that had caught in our adventurous hearts."}}]}
{"id":"p017","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p017-s0","tokens":[{"s":"夢","r":"ゆめ","v":"v0122"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"抱いた","r":"いだいた","v":"v0123","lemma":"抱く"},{"s":"その","v":"v0114"},{"s":"日","r":"ひ","v":"v0124"},{"s":"から"},{"s":"僕達","r":"ぼくたち","v":"v0012"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"冒険","r":"ぼうけん","v":"v0125"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"始まった","r":"はじまった","v":"v0126","lemma":"始まる"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"From the day we took up that dream, our adventure began."}}]}
{"id":"p018","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p018-s0","tokens":[{"s":"ハンター","v":"v0102"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"目指す","r":"めざす","v":"v0033"},{"s":"にあたり"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"僕達","r":"ぼくたち","v":"v0012"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"まず","v":"v0127"},{"s":"力","r":"ちから","v":"v0088"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"蓄えた","r":"たくわえた","v":"v0128","lemma":"蓄える"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"In setting out to become Hunters, we first built up our strength.","note":"〜にあたり is a formal connective meaning \"on the occasion of / when undertaking ~\". It marks a deliberate threshold moment, more weighty than a casual 〜時 (when).","grammar":["g-ni-atari"]}},{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p018-s1","tokens":[{"s":"互い","r":"たがい","v":"v0129"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"役割","r":"やくわり","v":"v0130"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"決め","r":"きめ","v":"v0131","lemma":"決める"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"それぞれ","v":"v0132"},{"s":"一流","r":"いちりゅう","v":"v0133"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"ハンター","v":"v0102"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"なる","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"べく"},{"s":"切磋琢磨","r":"せっさたくま","v":"v0134"},{"s":"した","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"We decided our roles among ourselves and threw ourselves into training, each aiming to become a first-rate Hunter in their own right.","note":"〜べく is the literary purposive: \"in order to ~ / so as to ~.\" 切磋琢磨 is a four-character Sino-Japanese idiom (\"to grind and polish each other\"), used for friends or rivals who push each other to improve.","grammar":["g-beku"]}}]}
{"id":"p019","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p019-s0","tokens":[{"s":"勇敢","r":"ゆうかん","v":"v0046"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"無鉄砲","r":"むてっぽう","v":"v0042"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"腕っ節","r":"うでっぷし","v":"v0043"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"強い","r":"つよい","v":"v0044"},{"s":"男友達","r":"おとこともだち","v":"v0135"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"無双","r":"むそう","v":"v0136"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"『"},{"s":"剣士","r":"けんし","v":"v0137"},{"s":"』"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"なり","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"とても","v":"v0054"},{"s":"足","r":"あし","v":"v0055"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"速く","r":"はやく","v":"v0056","lemma":"速い"},{"s":"器用","r":"きよう","v":"v0057"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"友人","r":"ゆうじん","v":"v0020"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"罠","r":"わな","v":"v0138"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"看破","r":"かんぱ","v":"v0139"},{"s":"し","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"パーティ","v":"v0140"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"導く","r":"みちびく","v":"v0141"},{"s":"『"},{"s":"盗賊","r":"とうぞく","v":"v0142"},{"s":"』"},{"s":"("},{"s":"別に","r":"べつに","v":"v0143"},{"s":"泥棒","r":"どろぼう","v":"v0144"},{"s":"する","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"わけ","v":"v0145"},{"s":"じゃない"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"一般的","r":"いっぱんてき","v":"v0146"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"そう","v":"v0147"},{"s":"呼ばれる","r":"よばれる","v":"v0148","lemma":"呼ぶ"},{"s":")"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"なった","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"The brave, reckless, scrappy boy among us became an unmatched \"Swordsman\", and the swift, dexterous friend became a \"Thief\" who saw through traps and led the party (he wasn't actually robbing anyone — that's just what the role gets called).","note":"The narrator interrupts the description with a parenthetical aside in his own voice — a common light-novel device for sneaking in worldbuilding clarifications without breaking the prose. The aside protects the friend's reputation rather than describing his actions."}}]}
{"id":"p020","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p020-s0","tokens":[{"s":"そして","v":"v0149"},{"s":"それ","v":"v0063"},{"s":"以外","r":"いがい","v":"v0150"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"友人","r":"ゆうじん","v":"v0020"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"──"},{"s":"幸","r":"こう","v":"v0151"},{"s":"か"},{"s":"不幸","r":"ふこう","v":"v0152"},{"s":"か"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"友人達","r":"ゆうじんたち","v":"v0153"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"それぞれ","v":"v0132"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"ハンター","v":"v0102"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"必要","r":"ひつよう","v":"v0154"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"珠玉","r":"しゅぎょく","v":"v0155"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"才能","r":"さいのう","v":"v0156"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"持っていた","r":"もっていた","v":"v0157","lemma":"持つ"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"And as for the rest of our friends — for better or worse, every one of them turned out to possess a gem of a talent perfectly suited to a Hunter."}}]}
{"id":"p021","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p021-s0","tokens":[{"s":"その","v":"v0114"},{"s":"片鱗","r":"へんりん","v":"v0158"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"ハンター","v":"v0102"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"なる","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"前","r":"まえ","v":"v0159"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"役割","r":"やくわり","v":"v0130"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"分けて","r":"わけて","v":"v0160","lemma":"分ける"},{"s":"訓練","r":"くんれん","v":"v0161"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"行っている","r":"おこなっている","v":"v0162","lemma":"行う"},{"s":"段階","r":"だんかい","v":"v0163"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"既に","r":"すでに","v":"v0164"},{"s":"明らか","r":"あきらか","v":"v0165"},{"s":"だった"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Glimpses of those talents had already been obvious before any of us became Hunters, back when we were still training in our separate roles."}}]}
{"id":"p022","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p022-s0","tokens":[{"s":"才能","r":"さいのう","v":"v0156"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"なかった"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"僕","r":"ぼく","v":"v0074"},{"s":"だけ"},{"s":"だった"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"I was the only one without any talent."}}]}
{"id":"p023","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p023-s0","tokens":[{"s":"たった","v":"v0166"},{"s":"一人","r":"ひとり","v":"v0022"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"何","r":"なに","v":"v0167"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"やらせても","v":"v0168","lemma":"やる"},{"s":"人並み","r":"ひとなみ","v":"v0169"},{"s":"以下","r":"いか","v":"v0170"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"しか"},{"s":"なれなかった","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"僕","r":"ぼく","v":"v0074"},{"s":"だけ"},{"s":"だった"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Just one of us — the one who, no matter what he was given to do, could never rise above below-average — was me, and only me.","note":"〜しか…ない (here しかなれなかった) is an exclusive negative: \"could only become below-average\". Combined with たった一人 and 僕だけだった, the sentence stacks three different ways of saying \"only me\" — a deliberate piling-on for emotional weight."}}]}
{"id":"p024","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p024-s0","tokens":[{"s":"四人","r":"よにん","v":"v0171"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"友人","r":"ゆうじん","v":"v0020"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"妹","r":"いもうと","v":"v0073"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"僕","r":"ぼく","v":"v0074"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Four friends, my sister, and me."}},{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p024-s1","tokens":[{"s":"六人","r":"ろくにん","v":"v0040"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"中","r":"なか","v":"v0109"},{"s":"で"},{"s":"僕","r":"ぼく","v":"v0074"},{"s":"だけ"},{"s":"だった"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Of those six, only me.","note":"The original is a verbless fragment — 僕だけだった with no stated subject or verb of action. It's deliberately incomplete, the rhetorical drumbeat of \"only me\" carrying over from the previous sentence and into the next."}},{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p024-s2","tokens":[{"s":"たった","v":"v0166"},{"s":"一人","r":"ひとり","v":"v0022"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"僕","r":"ぼく","v":"v0074"},{"s":"だけ"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"何","r":"なに","v":"v0167"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"できなかった","v":"v0121","lemma":"できる"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Just one of us — only me — could do nothing at all."}}]}
{"id":"p025","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p025-s0","tokens":[{"s":"英雄","r":"えいゆう","v":"v0037"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"なる","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"道","r":"みち","v":"v0172"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"見えなかった","r":"みえなかった","v":"v0173","lemma":"見える"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"僕","r":"ぼく","v":"v0074"},{"s":"だけ"},{"s":"だった"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"I was the only one who couldn't see the road that led to becoming a hero."}}]}
{"id":"p026","sentences":[{"id":"00-nageki-no-bourei-1-p026-s0","tokens":[{"s":"もう","v":"v0174"},{"s":"五年","r":"ごねん","v":"v0175"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"前","r":"まえ","v":"v0159"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"話","r":"はなし","v":"v0010"},{"s":"だ"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"It's a story from five whole years ago now."}}]}
